<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><em>We are strong advocates for focusing first on <span style="color: #222222;background-color: var(--paletteColor5, #E9EBEC)" class="stk-highlight"><strong>learning proper exercise form</strong></span> before worrying about the amount you’re lifting. This applies to <span style="color: #222222;background-color: var(--paletteColor5, #E9EBEC)" class="stk-highlight"><strong>all levels of gym goers</strong></span>, not just beginners.</em></p></blockquote>
