</div></div>
<p>“How To” Tips:</p>
<ul><li>Squeeze your chest muscles on both the descent (eccentric phase) and press (concentric phase). Try to mentally shut down the triceps as much as possible to force your chest to do the work.</li><li>Forearms should remain perpendicular to resistance, hands directly in front of elbows.</li></ul>
<h4><strong>Underhand Chest Press</strong></h4>
