</div></div>
<p>“How To” Tips:</p>
<ul><li>Let your arms straighten at the bottom of each rep without relaxing your arms.</li><li>Avoid rocking back and forth.</li><li>Do your best to keep elbows close to your body throughout each rep.</li><li>Squeeze your biceps for a tight pause at the top of each rep.</li></ul>
