<ul><li>You can do triceps extensions by lying on a flat bench, or on a decline bench. Decline is more challenging.</li><li>Upper arms should remain as rigid and still as possible, bending only at the elbows. Only the forearms should be moving.</li><li>Squeeze your triceps hard at the top of each rep.</li></ul>
