</div></div></div>
</div></div>
<p>“How To” Tips”</p>
<ul><li>We recommend the EZ Curl cable attachment.</li><li>Stand facing the cable stack and back away from the machine a full step.</li><li>Bend forward at the waist, so that you’re facing the floor. Extend your arms toward the machine.</li><li>Row backward, raising slightly upward as the bar passes in front of your face and chest.</li><li>Keep your elbows near your body and pull hard so that your elbows finish slightly behind the level of your back.</li><li>Let your shoulder blades rotate toward the machine at the beginning of each rep for a complete ROM.</li></ul>
<h4><strong>The Chest Supported Dumbbell Row</strong></h4>
<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
