</div></div></div>
</div></div>
<p>“How To” Tips:</p>
<ul><li>Stand with heels on a small barbell plate. This will help you find the groove during the squat.</li><li>Your upper body should remain as upright as possible.</li></ul>
<h4><strong>The Hex Bar Squat</strong> (Trab Bar Squat)</h4>
